{"tid":303292,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣去追返一個曾經好熟既人","createTime":"2017-06-30T05:15:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T09:15:31.000Z","uid":29163,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f1ad5d113e57a8563afc89e78ccb2f0097827671","tid":303292,"uid":29163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:15:22.000Z","msg":"係若干年前(唔講幾多年了費事比人起底)<br />\n有一個女仔同我好熟好fd,而佢亦一直知道我鐘意佢<br />\n但當年既我年少氣盛,牌氣好差好大,加上自卑心作祟,控制慾好強<br />\n所以成日同佢鬧交,我知道我on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我唔應該話佢鬧佢,因為每次好大程度上其實係我錯<br />\n最終搞到佢頂唔順唔再理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,我知我on9,我認我真係好撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家諗返真係怪自己on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明佢已經好忍讓但我仲得寸進尺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ...<br />\n但我咁耐以黎都放唔低佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,有咩方法令佢對我改觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我唔知應該點樣同佢講野好,所以一路搵佢都係用d派膠既語氣同佢講野(唔係有心針對波台,但我一路都係用波台班巴打既語氣同佢講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n但佢次次都hea鳩我,係咪除左投胎再無機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一諗返起以前佢同我講既野就好撚sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢仲會笑鳩我暗爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:佢從來都唔係我女朋友"},{"pid":"0c7fbd672f47dd123ec46dd5046d842c703a4530","tid":303292,"uid":29163,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:15:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f71453376d04ed092c09b4152a691700dcfd4e7e","